課程概述 Course Description
       講述工業用炸藥的組成，種類，化學反應方式，引爆方法，工程應用，爆炸震波之量測及作業安全。
工程應用集中於隧道開炸及露天礦山開炸兩類，講述爆破的岩石破壞理論，爆破設計方式，到工程實務應用。
•	The application will focus on tunnel and surface mine blasting.  It will discuss on rock fracture theory, breaking mechanism, blasting design method and field application.
Introduce the present types of commercial explosives, their chemical composition, reaction, initiating method, engineering application, blasting wave monitoring, and operation safety.
    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives


